content.detailedDescription: I was at work photographing some flowering trees. the weather was generally sunny with occasional low clouds crossing the sun. i was waiting for a mass of clouds to pass so that bright sun would return so i could take photos. i looked up to where the sun was behind the clouds. at that moment i noticed a vey fast moving aircraft. it was white colored and flying well above the cloud level. it appeared to resemble a concord jet but with sleeker wings and no tail, just a blended body. i saw it for 10 seconds at the most. i turned my camera back on but by that time it had flown behind the cloud bank. since it was flying very rapidly and in a straight line i got my camera ready to photograph it once it came by the other side. but it never appeared. i heard no noise and saw no contrails. it was traveling from southeast to northwest.Where i was is in the flight path for jets landing at orlando international airport which is appx 10 miles south of the sighting location. they are usually low enough where often you can make out the airline name or logo on the jet. i also see jet traffic flying over at higher altitudes. this unknown aircraft seemed to be flying higher than commercial jets. i did not notice any lighting or any markings or insigna. just a white colored aircraft. from my vantage point the size in the sky was very small, maybe aspirin size from an outstretched hand. afterwards i watched and scanned around for about 5 minutes and saw nothing. i have attached a rough sketch i made of what i saw.
content.summary: Fast flying, white colored delta wing aircraft

content.detailedDescription: My viewing happened aprox july 2013, it was a hot summer day with clear blue sky's no clouds at all! in july 2013 when i was standing on my back yard deck with my girlfriend myself at the time ( 45 yrs old, girlfriend 57 yrs old ) having a cigarette at 2:00pm, when i looked up in the sky at a 45 degree angle & saw a black dot sitting in the sky not moving at all. we watched it for 2 min then it zigg zagged 3 times then shot over our house (north) in a split second. we looked at each other and couldn't believe it! my girlfriend after that had finished her cigarette and went back in house, then 5 min later it was back in the same spot in sky so i called my girlfriend back outside, she saw it also again 1 min after we were looking at it! it zigg zagged 3 times again then went (south) towards toronto in a split second vanished.
content.summary: Myself and girlfriend witnessed clear blue sky black object twice 5 min apart.

content.detailedDescription: I was out walking my dog in larimer county colorado. i saw four ufos in pattern formation descend from the north at high speed and head south in a straight-line at an unbelievable speed. the ufos seemd to consist of a large glowing amber orb as the main body with two smaller same colored orbs positioned on the right and on the left in the front of the body. the second from the left seamed to be leading and by the way the craft seemed to accelerate before the others and slight inperfections in their flight pattern they seemed to be manned craft. if i had to make my best the craft stopped their decent at maybe 20-25k feet and then accelerated in a straight path from over my head to south and beyond the horizon in 2 or 3 seconds. this happened at approximately 18:56 mtn on 2/25/18. someone else had to of seen this.
content.summary: I saw four ufos in pattern formation descend from the north at high speed and head south in a straight-line at an unbelievable speed.

content.detailedDescription:
I see these orb ufos all the time. usually it’s more occasional but since the end of january 2018 i have seen them every night with the exception of clouds or rain. every clear night i see between 1 and 10 of these and occasionally i will see other craft, whether unexplainable or man-made, such as helicopters or large fast planes or jets. following is an excerpt from my ufo log i've been keeping for the last 5-6 years. 

feb 10 6:20-9 pm - approx 5 seen
6:20- one large orb came from top of orion to the north, caught sight of it just before it disappeared. saw 2 more small ones. then from the west at about 7:01-7:05 saw very large orb, yellowish color, no blinking, came straight toward me to the southeast. flew right over my head!!!! that’s why i decided to report it.  it didn’t look very high above me, definitely lower than an airplane. got lots photos, in photos it looks white, didn’t show up in video though. so amazingly bright and incredible!!! i was leaning backwards trying to get pics cuz it was straight overhead. wow. 
had a strange feeling it could see me or sense me. odd. it went behind the large trees on east side of yard and disappeared or just kept going though i couldn’t see it, not sure. i felt like it was a special appearance just for me, like the fireballs. how come no one on the hwy saw them? there have been so many lately. i saw one every night for 6 days straight. a weird thing i should mention; two hours before these sightings, two black hawk helicopters flew from north to south down the coast. my husband  says that if there are two, it means someone important is in one of them. when training they only use one. we are several hundred miles from nearest air force base. have heard lots of large jets around lately too. the photos i got of the large orb are tic tac shaped, just like the one in the disclosure video the air force got. they called it the tic tac and said they had been tracking them for two weeks before finally getting footage and visual sightings. perhaps these helicopters were tracking them? 

since this sighting i’ve continued to see them every clear night. i will post more sightings and photos/videos.
content.summary: Saw 5 orb type ufos, the big one i’m reporting flew right over my head, got photos

content.detailedDescription: I was driving home from work. i turned on to robinson road off of post oak lane in denton, tx. when there was a break in the houses to my left, i expect it was over the golf course, i soon noticed what appeared to be the moon, it was very large and somewhat ominous looking. i rolled down my window to get a better look as i passed. it was not a full moon, but maybe 80% or so. i recall seeing moon-like features to its surface. i can't explicitly say craters, i just remember it being so much like the moon that i accepted it as such and had no reason to doubt it. i had this weird sense, even though it wasn't clear, this moon gave off like a dreary/foggy vibe, and i began wondering "what if the moon affects our emotions and we don't even realize it?" and having imaginings of a werewolf transformation. which was odd, because in retrospect i was feeling unusually agitated at work that day and on the drive home. but i wrote it off and continued driving. then, less than 1/4 mile down the street, i noticed to the right, on the opposite side of the road, was a particularly mundane and typical looking moon. when i got home, i intended to climb onto the roof and see if i could see it, but it was too slick from rain and too dark to do that safely. after 5 minutes or less, i decided to drive back out and see if i could see it again, maybe get a video, although my phone was on its last leg. i drove back to the beginning of robinson, turned around to come back, and could not find the big moon again, despite going back multiple times. when i came closer to home, i noticed i could also no longer see the smaller, more mundane moon from my car from any vantage. a bit perplexed, i decided to go home, having been wondering if i was losing it the entire time. when i got back home, i was surprised to see that the excursion took 30 minutes, as that's on the longer end of time that it would normally take me to get home from work, and it did not seem like i was looking for these things for that long. as i recall, these objects, while both passable for the moon, were not identical. i do recall the color being similar if not the same, but the larger one seemed to be more eclipsed, and the surface details i recall being more vibrant/detailed than the smaller one. not only that, but only the larger one gave me an ominous feeling about it - almost like this thing coulda been in the thriller video.
content.summary: I saw a peculiar, large moon to the left of the road, then shortly thereafter i saw a typical moon on the right side of the road.

content.detailedDescription:
February 20, 2018, we (2 persons) were driving on the highway a1 in the direction of zürich. before we reached the town önsingen,  we saw a grey small spot high in the sky, on the right sight of the highway a1, under the clouds. the object was "glued" in the sky. it didn't move at all.

we took the next exit at önsingen and parked the car to observe the object for another 15 minutes. it didn't move. the other person could recognize two oval objects, one on top of the other. the object on top was bigger. there was no connection visible between them.

after 15 minutes, we had to leave. the object didn't move during the whole 30 minutes of the observation. i tried to take some pictures and video recordings with an iphone. it wasn't neither an airplane, nor a balloon nor a drone.

after several hours we drove the same way back. it was still daytime, but the clouds were heavier. we took the same exit at önsingen. the object was gone or invisible in the clouds. we drove "under" the presumed location for another hour, but didn't see any sign of it.

at home i saw that, on the video recording, the object was visible as a really tiny grey dot in the cloudy sky. the shape was not recognizable. the person who accompagnied me, draw a sketch of the two oval shaped objects he saw.
content.summary: Distand oval-shaped ufo over highway a1 in switzerland

content.detailedDescription: It was 7:15pm when i left the house and began driving west up the hill on del webb dr.To the summit clubhouse for an event. i immediately noticed the large craft in front of my car above the houses in front of me because it was flying too low and i thought it was going to crash into the neighborhood.  i was going 30-35 miles per hour and the craft stayed the same distance from me so it was also going very slow.  i thought when it didn't crash into any homes that it was perhaps in trouble trying to land at the las vegas airport. however, it continued to move at the same speed but just a tad higher all the way to the top of the hill where i was going.  when i pulled into the parking lot i saw that the craft turned a little more to the north since it had been traveling west all the way up the hill.  the craft had three red lights - one on the left side, one on the right side and one in the middle.  this is why i originally thought it might be a large military aircraft but it was flying too low and there was not a sound coming from the craft.  then as i attempted to make out the shape it reminded me of the very large "v" shaped object i had seen when the craft was over phoenix, arizona.  the entire sighting took about 12 minutes and the night was very clear.
content.summary: Looked like the large craft the size of several football fields that was seen over phoenix arizona several years ago.

content.detailedDescription: In this video i was driving to work early in the morning and i started hearing this whir sound something like the sound of an old car engine trying to turn over but can’t because of battery/alternator...Im looking all around me to see if i could locate the sound then realized the sound was from above. it was 4:39am on a snowy colorado morning and i’m pretty much the only car on the road and i knew it wasn’t an airplane due to the time of day. so i grab my phone and start to record a video of the night/morning sky, i record a minute of video and at the time this was happening i couldn’t see anything with my own eyes. when i get to work moments later i looked at the video and my mouth hit the floor.  i have no idea what this is or even how to describe it.
content.summary: Entity hovers and takes flight path of my direction

content.summary: Explosion and then white chem trail descending downward and west over golden gate

content.detailedDescription: This happened about 5 years ago but i still remember it like it was yesterday. i was in my room on the second floor of my house,my wife was laying on the bed watching tv and i was looking out the window,with my forearms on the window with my head sticking out i get a good view of the sky and just pryor to that i was watching a few videos on how to remote view and in a way i was trying to see if i could make some kind of contact now i'm not saying that because of remote viewing i had this experience but it could be a factor.Now as i was looking out my window for about 30 min out of nowhere a black triangle appeared right in front of me right above a tree we have in front and it's about the size of our roof if not smaller and this thing was right above that so it was close,at first my brain was trying to figure out if it was a blimp,plane idk anything but quickly realized it was none of those things..It made no noise it was so black i could just see the shape of the lights and the craft but no detail to it as if it was all one peice of material.The lights looked l shapped and they kind of over lapped each other..It had these lights on each corner of the craft..When it went directly above me they almost looked like x's and the light looked like no other light i've seen before i mean it was white but a white i've never seen before..It's not like the light we see when we turn on a light bulb..So as it hoovered over my house i leaned out as far as i could unroll i couldn't see it anymore then i ran out but it was gone
content.summary: Black triangle appeared out of nowhere right in front of my eyes the slowly hoovered over my house

content.detailedDescription: My fiancée and i were driving home after picking up food. in las vegas nv. we noticed 3 lights in the sky which from a distance, at first glance, it appeared to be 3 planes flying in unison. once the craft came closer and as we got a better view. we saw it was one massive craft. i took my phone out and tried to video it. we were moving so it was difficult to capture. the craft made no noise and at its lowest altitude appeared to be around 1,000 ft. it stopped and hovered abruptly and then continued on it’s path west towards red rock.
content.summary: Long flat craft which had 3 lights hovered and made no sound

content.detailedDescription: I was walking home around 9:30pm with my girlfriend at the time and as always im looking up at the stars. as we came around the corner i noticed the orange orb just hovering above a 2 story home. their was no noise it just hovered above the house. at first i thought my eyes were playing tricks on me but thanfully i wasnt alone. i wasnt sure what it was exactly but it was about the size of a small helicopter. it didnt have any features such as other lights, windows, wings, ect. i got so excited due to the fact it was my first sighting that i didnt take my phone out. i wish i would have. its something ill never forget. as i stood their watching this mysterious orange orb about 19 minutes in it started moving very slowly towards the east and at the 20 min mark it vanished. it made me think of harry potter and his invibility cloak. it was absolutely fascinating.
content.summary: Orange sphere silent stationary for 18 min then moved towards east vanished

content.detailedDescription: Temecula california 11:40 pm i was smoking in my back yard seated facing south. i felt strongly compelled to look to my left where i saw an eerily silent, triangular craft with two faintly color changing pulsating lights. it hovered above a neighbors house approximately 150 ft in the air, then moving forward very slowly. i was seemingly forced to look down for less than a second, looking back up again the craft was halfway across the sky and about 10,000 feet in elevation. then within a blink of an eye the craft was so far it dispares into the sky approximately 75 degrees above the horizon
content.summary: Silent triangle craft two large pulsating lights in rear of craft. hovered 150ft in air then shot across sky disappearing as a tiny dot high in sky
